<div style="width: 600px; max-height: 550px; overflow-x: auto;"><h1 class="green b_mar_ten">ECCC SPOTLIGHT LOUNGE PRESENTS: SECRET ORIGINS WITH GARTH ENNIS</h1>
	<p class="size11"><strong>Room: EMERALD CITY SPOTLIGHT LOUNGE (604)</strong><em><br/>Start: 2:40PM<br/>End: 3:35PM</em></p><br/>
	<p class="rte"><b>Garth Ennis</b> first gaining attention in the 90's with his work on "Judge Dredd", Garth continued his rise in popularity with brilliant runs on "The Demon", "Hitman" and "Hellblazer" but it was his run on "Preacher" that made him a super star! Join him as he speaks to Blair Butler (AOTS) about that historic book, his recently concluded run on "The Boys", his work on "The Punisher" and what his plans are for the all new "Red Team"!<br></p></div>